<view class="page">
  <view class="success-card card">
    <view class="success-icon">✓</view>
    <text class="h1">品牌信息已提交</text>
    <text class="lead">GeoGi 已收到资料，项目会自动进入品牌建档、问题生成和诊断准备流程。</text>
    <text wx:if="{{submission.clientId}}" class="success-id">客户编号：{{submission.clientId}}</text>
    <text wx:if="{{submission.projectId}}" class="success-id">项目编号：{{submission.projectId}}</text>
    <text wx:if="{{submission.notificationStatus}}" class="success-id muted-id">通知状态：{{submission.notificationStatus}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="section card next-card">
    <text class="block-title">预计完成时间</text>
    <text class="body estimate-copy">品牌档案和检测问题会先自动生成；完成 AI 平台问答后，报告初稿通常可在当天整理。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="section card next-card">
    <text class="block-title">接下来会发生什么</text>
    <view class="next-row" wx:for="{{nextSteps}}" wx:key="*this">
      <text class="next-num">0{{index + 1}}</text>
      <text>{{item}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section card contact-card">
    <text class="block-title">加速诊断</text>
    <text class="body">添加诊断顾问企业微信，可以更快确认品牌主体、服务范围和报告交付周期。</text>
    <button class="primary-button full-button" bindtap="goContact">添加诊断顾问企业微信</button>
    <button class="secondary-button full-button mine-button" bindtap="goMine">查看我的诊断</button>
  </view>

  <view class="section card article-card">
    <text class="block-title">等待期间可以先读</text>
    <view class="article-row" wx:for="{{articles}}" wx:key="id" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="openArticle">
      <text>{{item.title}}</text>
      <text class="arrow">›</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <button class="secondary-button full-button home-button" bindtap="goHome">返回首页</button>
</view>
